<L>__{exterior camp day}
<A>__{dom paulo and father diogo are standing beside dom paulo's table, all that remains of his headquarters on the beach.}
<C>__{father diogo}
<D>__{i will comfort them as best as i can.}
<C>__{dom paulo}
<D>__{you're staying with them?}
<A>__{father diogo hastens to correct this misunderstanding.}
<C>__{father diogo}
<D>__{no, no, i will comfort them before we leave. i think my place is with you...}
<A>__{two sailors, like stagehands, enter and remove the table, leaving dom paulo and father diogo propless on the beach.}
